text: Kelli Berglund (born February 9, 1996) is an American actress. She is known for playing Bree Davenport in the Disney XD series Lab Rats and its spin-off Lab Rats: Elite Force. In 2014, she played Mae Hartley in the Disney Channel Original Movie How to Build a Better Boy. She later played Carly Carson in the 2019 Starz television drama series Now Apocalypse. Berglund has been honored with many awards for her lyrical contemporary music and jazz. Berglund was born in Moorpark, California. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:American child actors Category:Actors from California Category:Living people
